# Part 15 — Windows Security Investigation

## Overview

This project demonstrates a hands-on security investigation in a Windows lab environment using Wazuh and Windows Event Logs. The objective is to identify suspicious activity, analyze relevant events, and document the investigation process.

---

## Objectives

- Detect suspicious activity
- Investigate Windows security events
- Correlate related log entries
- Document findings
- Map activity to MITRE ATT&CK

---

## Lab Environment

| Component | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| SIEM | Wazuh |
| Operating System | Windows 10 |
| Domain Controller | Windows Server 2022 |
| Hypervisor | Hyper-V |
| Log Sources | Windows Event Logs |

